data.text: @Lindax0101 @CBCToronto Because all those under 60 would get in their cars, drive to Ottawa and protest how stpuid this all is. Numbers always were skewed by the elderly. Science is clear; it is past time to open up.

@CBCToronto Why don’t you ever report the age groups?
